Take the person on the right and style it like the left image. Subject should be
slightly turned towards the camera like the person in the left photo. Wearing a
business casual outfit with subtle patterns or textures, displaying a confident smile
with direct eye contact. Illuminated by crisp, professional lighting with a soft fill
to reduce shadows, against a subtly textured or gradient light background. Their
expression conveys expertise and approachability. Executive portrait photography with
editorial polish. Shot with a Sony Alpha A7 III and an f/1.8 lens. Photorealistic,
8k. Square aspect ratio (1:1).
